author: Devon Jefferson
title: Kodak Black "Everything 1K" Video
text:
Posted by Devon Jefferson , Feb 9, 2017 at 07:51pm Subscribe to HNHH TV Kodak Black recruits Danielle Bregoli aka "Catch Me Outside" girl for the "Everything 1K" video. 
Danielle Bregoli is literally everywhere right now. The "Catch Me Outside" viral internet personality recently got rough with a woman on a Spirit Airlines flight and threatened TMZ reporters , and now, she's the star of Kodak Black 's video for "Everything 1K." 
In a strange turn of events, Black decided to leave himself out of the video and give all the shine to Bregoli. The video features Bregoli standing on top of a Rolls-Royce reciting Black's lyrics like a true MC. While this seems like an unlikely move for Kodak Black, it's definitely a come-up for Danielle Bregoli.
